# Environment Template for Skin Cancer Detection

## Backend (.env or docker-compose override)

SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key_here
MONGO_URI=mongodb://mongo:27017/skin_cancer
ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=1440
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173,http://localhost:3000
MODEL_PATH=/app/model/skin_cancer.onnx
MAX_UPLOAD_SIZE=5242880
ALLOWED_IMAGE_TYPES=image/jpeg,image/png

## Frontend (.env or .env.local)

VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/api

## Docker Compose

All above values can be supplied via `docker-compose.yml` under `services.backend.environment` and `services.frontend.environment`.
